data: On the 15th of October, 19—, at four o’clock in the afternoon, in the garden of the Monte Pincio in Rome, sat a girl, no longer in the first flush of youth, Irene Mstinskaia.
Dostoevskaia, L. F. (Liubov Fedorovna), 1869-1926; Margolies, Vera [Translator]; Graham, Stephen, 1884-1975 [Author of introduction, etc.]
